<item>
            <title>[LU-4246] Test failure on test suite conf-sanity, subtest test_72</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4246</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Bob Glossman &amp;lt;bob.glossman@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/acaa49a4-4c5c-11e3-826a-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/acaa49a4-4c5c-11e3-826a-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;very high failure rate reported&lt;br/&gt;
Failure Rate: 32.00% of last 100 executions &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;all branches&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have to assume this is blocking a lot of testing.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_72 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;mount client failed&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: conf-sanity 72&lt;/p&gt;</description>
